divs: Sighting Details My husband and I took a look at the moon before going into the house for the night. As we looked into the western sky we observed a very bright object heading in a distinct eastern path. There was no sound and it was not a plane. The bright object was lower than a plane. We could not believe how fast it was traveling as we watched the object disappear over the hill.
